&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-title-input-label-inner&quot; class=&quot;docs-title-input-label-inner&quot;&gt;Director, Consumer Engagement &amp;amp; Advocacy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; New York, NY (Hybrid, 4x Week In-Office)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reporting to:&lt;/strong&gt; Chief Marketing Officer&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Department:&lt;/strong&gt; Influencer &amp;amp; Community&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salary:&lt;/strong&gt; $110k-$170k&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
